    <tbody>
      <tr><td>Earbuds dig into ears when side sleeping</td><td>Ultra-flat speakers are flush with the mask — zero pressure on ear canal</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Sleep masks shift and let light in overnight</td><td>Adjustable rear strap with secure clip keeps position through movement</td></tr>
      <tr><td>3D eye cups collapse and touch eyelids</td><td>Contoured foam cups stay lifted, protecting eyelash extensions and REM sleep</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Wired headphones = tangled cables in sheets</td><td>Bluetooth 5.0 — fully wireless, 10 meter range, stays connected through the night</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Volume control requires grabbing a phone</td><td>Onboard +/- buttons and play/pause on the mask itself</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
