<!-- §11 How to use -->
<h2>How to Set Up and Use the Boodlab Bluetooth Sleep Mask</h2>
<ol style="line-height:2;color:var(--foreground);">
  <li><strong>Charge fully before first use</strong> — plug in via USB and wait for the LED to stop flashing (about 2 hours)</li>
  <li><strong>Power on and enter pairing mode</strong> — hold the power button 3 seconds until the indicator flashes rapidly</li>
  <li><strong>Connect on your phone</strong> — open Bluetooth settings, select "Boodlab", confirm pairing. It reconnects automatically after the first time.</li>
  <li><strong>Adjust the strap</strong> — slide the rear adjuster until the mask sits snug across the bridge of your nose without squeezing your temples</li>
  <li><strong>Start your audio and sleep</strong> — use the onboard buttons to adjust volume without touching your phone</li>
</ol>

